{"_path":"/resident/r025","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"A7重劃區 - 公車候車站改善提案","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r025-04.jpeg","sequence":25,"category":"交通建設","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-11-08T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區-公車改善提案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區 - 公車改善提案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"公車站改善"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車站改善"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"候車站現況"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"候車站現況"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區樂善國小生活圈 目前公車 202, 606 都已穿越社區 給居民交通帶來很大的便利。 感謝議員們及市府的努力！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前樂善國小生活圈, 的樂善公園, 樂善國小, 樂學二三路口, 文達樂學路口站 及 中心商業區 的樂善寺站 都只有簡易的站牌，沒有正常候車站的基本設置！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"站牌設置處沒有用水泥鋪平。 中間是原有的草坪, 常因雨水, 垃圾, 狗糞無法站立。 人員候車時需要站在狹窄不足腳掌長的水泥柱上！一般常人也難保持平衡，對年長者及幼兒是很大考驗。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原有人行道就只能通過一人，如果佔用人行道會造成其他行人的通過困難。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"改善建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"無障礙設計*"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 候車亭設計應考量無障礙規劃，應讓上車區域能讓輪椅/嬰兒車能停放。 希望用水泥鋪平候車區域, 讓候車排隊與行人通行能兼容考量。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r025-04.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r025-04.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"資訊系統"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 目前樂善國小生活圈的公車利用率已經很高！希望能有電子看牌如下圖。 如此會讓居民知道等候時間, 可以增加使用率！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r025-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r025-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"無障礙公車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"無障礙公車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公車現況"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車現況"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"現階段 A7 重劃區 只有 202 公車具備低底盤設計, 提供輪椅/嬰兒車的乘坐空間。 因為 202 及 606 都是提供區域環形路線。希望能作為年長者輪椅及嬰兒車能到捷運站的最後一哩銜接公車。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"搭車時請參考 無障礙公車資訊： "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ebus.tycg.gov.tw/ebus/driving-map?route-group=cityBus"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市無障礙公車查詢"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://e-bus.ntpc.gov.tw/Accessibility/AccRelatedLinks"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雙北無障礙公車查詢"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"改善建議-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"無障礙公車需要具備的特點"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低地板設計：無障礙公車通常採用低地板設計，方便輪椅使用者進出。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升降平台或斜坡板：這些公車配備升降平台或斜坡板，使輪椅使用者能夠安全上下車。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全固定裝置：為了保障乘客安全，公車內會有專用的安全帶和固定裝置。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r025-0